          <h2>Dawn Brancheau</h2>
          <p>Dawn Therese Brancheau was a senior animal trainer at SeaWorld, who worked with orcas at SeaWorld Orlando for fifteen years, and was their poster girl. She was killed by an orca, Tilikum. </p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
