          <h2>Dave Worcester</h2>
          <p>Another former SeaWorld trainer to be attacked by an orca while working is Dave Worcester. Nepo, an preadolesent male orca, dragged the trainer to the bottom of the pool at the California location in the 1970's. But he did survive. </p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
