          <h2 class="featurette-heading">SeaWorld only has one thing in mind:  <span class="text-muted">money.</span></h2>
          <p class="lead">Animals are captured from the ocean or stolen from foreign waters. The men doing so describe netting the baby whales and killing the parents that would not leave without their child. After watching their parents die the young whales are shipped in large cargo boxes to the highest bidder, in most cases SeaWorld. </p>
