          <p class="lead">With the desire for adventure among us humans and the mystery of the ocean feeding into our curiosity, the idea of aquariums and water conservation parks are extremely popular. This makes it easy for companies such as Sea World to make such a profit off of exploiting animals. But the animals are the ones who have to pay the price.</p>
